resources.string:
Olpaka is not able to communicate with Ollama.

You could try to fix it by:
	• Making sure [Ollama is installed](https://ollama.com/download);
	• Checking it is running on port 11434;
	• Checking that [CORS is configured correctly](https://github.com/Otacon/olpaka/blob/main/docs/setup_cors.md);

As a last resort, you could try to restart the app.
